\[\widehat{\bm{dH}^{-1}}=\alpha\sum_{k=0}^{K}\bm{d}(\bm{I}-\alpha\bm{H})^{k}= \bm{dH}^{-1}-\alpha\sum_{k=K+1}^{\infty}\bm{d}(\bm{I}-\alpha\bm{H})^{k},\] (25)

